{"tid":2367016,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國麻省理工華裔教授涉未披露與中國關係遭起訴","createTime":"2021-01-15T04:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T13:17:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5e10a00e6205ed3f37304aacabf8a47522506a","tid":2367016,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"美國麻省理工華裔教授涉未披露與中國關係遭起訴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=420350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420350&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFg3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=fc0baa64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420350&h=5f92fb56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=420350</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國麻省理工一名華裔教授，被指申請聯邦政府資助時未透露與中國政府的關係，遭美國政府拘捕及起訴。<br />\n<br />\n56歲、在中國出生的陳剛是納米技術專家，現時是麻省理工納米工程實驗室負責人。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦檢控人員指陳剛為多個中國實體擔任職務，包括出任中國政府的海外專家，又指陳剛與研究團隊收取的外國款項中部分來自中國政府，但他在申請美國能源部撥款時未有根據規定披露與中國有關的資料。<br />\n<br />\n陳剛已獲准保釋，他的代表律師說，當事人將全力反擊指控，麻省理工亦發聲明指對事件感到不安。"},{"pid":"78401801c28ca3661c05c39d046bf26f8c7a4c07","tid":2367016,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c47c00e5cea26b9ba4f8cc4b4751a7a60e54ec0","tid":2367016,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"在中國出生的陳剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f562a52ff32d0114afdcd227e5090f24f0652333","tid":2367016,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac